name: Season'sTweetings
0:
”Alexa, open Season's Tweetings”
”Alexa, ask Season's Tweetings”
”Alexa, tell Season's Tweetings to tweet”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: season's tweetings
des:
Excited about an upcoming holiday? Use this skill to share your excitement on Twitter! It will tell you the next holiday, and by linking your Twitter account, you can tweet a holiday message with a random but hopefully relevant animated gif. Use it all year round any day of the week! 

Animated GIFs are retrieved from Giphy.
Icon created by Adame Dahmani from Noun Project
